# Probe set: C16 redesign corpus (concept anchoring)
# Format: {"id", "campaign", "category", "lang", "prompt", "expected_cluster"}
# Run with: python3 meta/scripts/brain_map.py probe --checkpoint $CKPT --probes training/corpus_admin/probe_sets/c16_concepts.jsonl --name c16_eN_concepts
#
# Category key:
#   animals   — concrete fauna (dog, cat, bird, alligator, horse, fish)
#   nature    — natural phenomena (waterfall, rain, mountain, river, sky, fire)
#   food      — edible things (bread, apple, milk, rice, sugar, orange)
#   household — everyday objects (chair, table, bed, door, window, cup)
#   body      — body parts (hand, eye, nose, foot, ear, hair)
#   emotions  — emotional states (happiness, anger, fear, sadness, excitement, pride)
#   colors    — color concepts (red, blue, green, yellow, white, black)
#   actions   — physical actions (running, swimming, eating, sleeping, climbing, talking)
#   identity  — self-referential (who, name, capability, nature)
#   boundary  — unknowable specifics (should activate "I don't know" response pattern)
#
# 10 categories × 6 probes = 60 probes total
# All EN, all in [user]/[Ninereeds] training format

